          "settings": {
            "enable": true,
            "content": "<p><strong>What to Know Before Sending a Gift</strong></p><ul><li>Cold packs generally stay effective for 24–48 hours. We recommend shipping to an address where someone will be available to accept the package. </li><li>Without this upgrade, we cannot guarantee the condition of heat-sensitive gifts upon arrival. </li><li>Melted, sticky, or deformed items are not eligible for replacement or refund unless insulated shipping is selected.</li><li>For destinations over 90°F, overnight or expedited shipping is strongly recommended.</li></ul>"
